metadata.name: BrokeBeaglez #1
metadata.description: BrokeBeaglez is a collection of 3333 generative NFTs. By applying a degen Snoopy image, the artist aims to show the struggle that young millennials and Gen Z are facing when they try to establish their identity and build a career in today's world. The theme will be conveyed through a story about a beagle with dissociative identity disorder attempting to kill his 3333 alters.
